<br>
The wall thing is for real, sit in the center at all times. <br>
<br>
Keep casting till you snare, make a hotkey <br>
/ooc %t is snared <br>
if you cant get a snare to stick tell people.<br>
<br>
Don't use shout channel, only the raid leader is allowed to use that channel.<br>
<br>
You will be a back-up healer. So make target keys for people who may need you, even if they are not in your group. A target key is <br>
<br>
/target Mooky<br>
<br>
And it will find me in a sea of people<br>
<br>
IF you get attacked don't run, buy one for the team. With 49+ rezzes you won't lose to much exp.<br>
<br>
Load up some stun type spells. The clerics usually don't have the manna, but remember Stuns will get you aggroed. Start stunning, the clerics (mobs) so they dont CH themselves, or gate.<br>
<br>
You will have a main tank and a monk. The monk will pull the tank will tag a mob. The tank will absorb punishment while he is building up aggro, in this time no one does anything. The MA (main assist) will have a hotkey that says Attack %t now! Then you start attacking.<br>
<br>
I like druids in my group cause they are some damage dealers, they often get our group exp! If they call a cleric camp (crash camp) Start unloading on anything close to the cleric, burn em down. Dying with full mana is BAD! I was in a crash camp last night and none of us managed to camp. The CR went text-book but we lost the camp, an hour and the spirit.<br>
<br>
You'll think wow, this is easy - and suddenly something will go wrong - never let your guard down. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=26450.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=26450.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26450.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=26450.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.threadControl?topicID=26450.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26450.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26450.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsg